tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  race VARCHAR(50),
  income FLOAT,
  education_level VARCHAR(50),
  program_suggestions TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
  income INT
);

CREATE TABLE educational_programs (
  program_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(100),
  target_population VARCHAR(100),
  program_type VARCHAR(50),
  program_duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(255),
  ethnicity VARCHAR(255),
  location VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE educational_background (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  demographic_id INT,
  education_level VARCHAR(255),
  specialized_training BOOLEAN,
  FOREIGN KEY (demographic_id) REFERENCES demographics(id)
);

CREATE TABLE program_enrollment (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  demographic_id INT,
  program_name VARCHAR(255),
  enrollment_date DATE,
  status VARCHAR(255),
  FOREIGN KEY (demographic_id) REFERENCES demographics(id)
);

CREATE TABLE program_participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR,
  participant_age INT,
  program_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES educational_programs(program_id)
);

CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
  student_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR,
  ethnicity VARCHAR,
  income DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE education_programs (
  program_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR,
  program_type VARCHAR,
  target_population VARCHAR,
  start_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE program_participants (
  participation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  student_id UUID REFERENCES demographic_data(student_id),
  program_id UUID REFERENCES education_programs(program_id),
  enrollment_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE program_evaluations (
  evaluation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  participation_id UUID REFERENCES program_participants(participation_id),
  evaluation_date DATE,
  feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE program_performance (
  performance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id UUID REFERENCES education_programs(program_id),
  success_rate DECIMAL,
  impact_analysis TEXT
)
